---
description: "Monorepo layout: Nuxt web + Laravel api"
alwaysApply: true
---

Repository layout (authoritative):
- /apps/web  => Nuxt 3 + Vue 3 + TypeScript (pnpm)
- /apps/api  => Laravel + PHP + MySQL (composer)
- /packages  => optional shared libs

Never collapse web+api into one app. Keep boundaries clean:
- Web calls API via HTTP (or a defined internal interface), not direct DB access.
- DB migrations live under /apps/api only.
